headline: Morgan Stanley sees 'severe financial risk' for California utilities amid wildfire
summary: Investing.com -- Morgan Stanley warned of significant financial risk for California utilities, citing concerns that the state's wildfire fund may no longer be sufficient to protect companies from catastrophic liabilities.
